  "title": "Operations Planning Manager (Aerospace, Up to $15,000)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Translate demand forecasts and customer orders into executable production plans.</li><li>Ensure material, labor, and machine capacity plans support delivery targets.</li><li>Act as the primary planning interface for program management and customer-facing teams.</li><li>Identify risks related to capacity, materials, or demand volatility and implement mitigation plans.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Business or equivalent</li><li>At least 5 years of experience in <strong>production planning or supply chain in aerospace industry.</strong></li><li>Proficiency with ERP/MRP systems and advanced planning tools.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
